Hubby‘s 1st attempt making lasagna and dough from scratch too since he couldn’t find any lasagna pasta after visiting 5 supermarkets! Everywhere is out of stock!!!.
.
Surprisingly his homemade beef lasagna turned out to be so delicious and we enjoyed it so much! 🤩😋😋😋.
.
He didn’t follow any recipe at all as everything was made by feel. He only asked me what type of flour to use and what temperature to use when baking. Yes, that’s all! Since everything was estimated, I can’t replicate it, so sad! 😭😭😭
.
